Name: WARP-TEK
About the game: WARP-TEK is a horizontal space shooter wherein you have to rescue your pet after it got abducted by aliens and consequently imprisoned on a distant planet. In this game, you will find: Over 20 boss types! 30+ enemy types! A hell of a lot of colours More than 25 weapons to collect and play with! References to other indie games!( Squirm , The Misadventures of Melon ) A warm feeling of satisfaction knowing that you're supporting a happy lil' indie boy!
